        {
            "id": 6009942,
            "title": "馬斯克 川普X上吵翻天 白宮助理急忙安排兩人周五通話 特斯拉應聲漲5%",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>美國《政客新聞網 (Politico)》周四 (5 日) 報導，白宮助手計劃安排川普總統和馬斯克周五進行電話會議，試圖緩和兩人之間激烈的公開爭執。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009942%2Fl%2F9423db55c7e6730ef0b7bd8ff9d91de8.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009942%2Fl%2F9423db55c7e6730ef0b7bd8ff9d91de8.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009942%2Fl%2F9423db55c7e6730ef0b7bd8ff9d91de8.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009942%2Fl%2F9423db55c7e6730ef0b7bd8ff9d91de8.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009942%2Fl%2F9423db55c7e6730ef0b7bd8ff9d91de8.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009942%2Fl%2F9423db55c7e6730ef0b7bd8ff9d91de8.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009942%2Fl%2F9423db55c7e6730ef0b7bd8ff9d91de8.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009942%2Fl%2F9423db55c7e6730ef0b7bd8ff9d91de8.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009942%2Fl%2F9423db55c7e6730ef0b7bd8ff9d91de8.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009942%2Fl%2F9423db55c7e6730ef0b7bd8ff9d91de8.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009942%2Fl%2F9423db55c7e6730ef0b7bd8ff9d91de8.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009942%2Fl%2F9423db55c7e6730ef0b7bd8ff9d91de8.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009942%2Fl%2F9423db55c7e6730ef0b7bd8ff9d91de8.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009942%2Fl%2F9423db55c7e6730ef0b7bd8ff9d91de8.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009942%2Fl%2F9423db55c7e6730ef0b7bd8ff9d91de8.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009942%2Fl%2F9423db55c7e6730ef0b7bd8ff9d91de8.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009942%2Fl%2F9423db55c7e6730ef0b7bd8ff9d91de8.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">(圖：shutterstock)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>該消息似乎提振了特斯拉股價。周四交易時間，由於川普與馬斯克在 X 上相互怒斥，川普威脅撤除政府給予馬斯克旗下企業的訂單，特斯拉股價周四收盤暴跌逾 14%，但在《Politico》報導發布後，特斯拉 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TSLA:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TSLA\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TSLA-US</a>) 盤後一度上漲 5%，報每股 298.64 美元。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>報導指出，川普在接受電話採訪時，曾對自己與馬斯克之間的爭執表現出「漠不關心」的態度。另外，根據報導，白宮助理正努力緩和兩人劍拔弩張的氣氛，安排兩人於周五進行電話會談。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>馬斯克和川普之間日益加劇的爭執在周四達到頂峰，兩人在社群媒體上互相人身攻擊。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>這場糾紛在短短幾個小時內就導致特斯拉市值蒸發約 1,​​500 億美元，給這家電動車製造商的股價帶來更大壓力。截至目前，特斯拉股價已下跌約 25%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>雖然特斯拉最初受益於馬斯克在白宮日益增長的影響力，但馬斯克與川普之間的裂痕可能會扭轉這一趨勢，尤其是在川普對馬斯克和這家電動車製造商採取更多政策行動的情況下。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
